com.safenetinc.jcprov.constants

Class CKD

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.safenetinc.jcprov.constants.CKD

  • public class CKD
extends java.lang.Object
    Class defining ProtectToolkit C CKD_ constants - Elliptic Curve Key Derivation Functions.

    Further information concerning the various key derivation values is provided in the PKCS#11 standard and the Programmers Manual.
